**HackVSIT 5.0**, hosted at *[Vivekananda institute of Professional Studies (VIPS)](https://vipstc.edu.in/)*, isn’t just a hackathon — its an innovation extravaganza! Organised by [ACE](https://vipsace.org), this event is designed to promote creativity in coding, design, and innovation while providing a platform for technical skills and inspiring real - world solutions. We're all about collaboration, pushing boundaries, and inspiring real-world solutions. What are you waiting for? Seize the opportunity and join us at [HackVSIT 5.0](https://hack-vsit.tech/)!

Got any queries? Ask us on [Discord](https://discord.gg/zZNrgktFzP).

